---
---
<section id="mercado" class="relative isolate mt-32 sm:mt-56">
  <!-- Testimonial-like dark section for market context -->
  <div class="bg-gray-900 py-20 sm:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-7xl flex-col items-center gap-x-8 gap-y-10 px-6 sm:gap-y-8 lg:px-8 xl:flex-row xl:items-stretch">
      <!-- Left: Market data -->
      <div class="w-full max-w-2xl xl:max-w-none xl:flex-auto xl:px-8 xl:py-12">
        <div class="relative isolate">
          <h2 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-eco-green-light">Oportunidad de mercado</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">Una oportunidad en el momento justo</p>

          <p class="mt-6 text-lg/8 text-gray-300">El mercado global de smart waste management esta valorado en USD 3.1 mil millones (2025) con crecimiento anual del 20%.</p>

          <dl class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-6 sm:grid-cols-3">
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-2 border-l border-white/15 pl-6">
              <dt class="text-sm/6 text-gray-400">Alcaldias con necesidades de optimizacion</dt>
              <dd class="order-first text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">16</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-2 border-l border-white/15 pl-6">
              <dt class="text-sm/6 text-gray-400">Separacion obligatoria de residuos</dt>
              <dd class="order-first text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">Ene 2026</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-2 border-l border-white/15 pl-6">
              <dt class="text-sm/6 text-gray-400">Sistemas inteligentes desplegados en Mexico</dt>
              <dd class="order-first text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">0</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>

          <p class="mt-8 text-sm/6 text-gray-400">Mexico aun no tiene adopcion significativa de smart waste management. EcoRuta llega como primer movimiento en el mercado mexicano.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Differentiators -->
      <div class="w-full max-w-2xl xl:max-w-md xl:flex-none">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 p-6 sm:p-8 ring-1 ring-white/10">
          <h3 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-white mb-6">Por que EcoRuta es diferente</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-300">
            <li class="flex gap-x-3">
              <svg class="size-5 flex-none text-eco-green-light mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
              <span><strong class="text-white">IA Generativa como interfaz</strong> — ningun competidor lo tiene</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-x-3">
              <svg class="size-5 flex-none text-eco-green-light mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
              <span><strong class="text-white">Sin hardware propietario</strong> — funciona con cualquier sensor IoT</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-x-3">
              <svg class="size-5 flex-none text-eco-green-light mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
              <span><strong class="text-white">Contexto mexicano</strong> — espanol nativo, alcaldias, regulacion local</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-x-3">
              <svg class="size-5 flex-none text-eco-green-light mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
              <span><strong class="text-white">Triple fuente de datos</strong> — sensores + reportes + historicos</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-x-3">
              <svg class="size-5 flex-none text-eco-green-light mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
              <span><strong class="text-white">Costo de entrada bajo</strong> — modelo SaaS, sin contenedores de $4,000 USD</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
